Package: rcrtan
Type: Package
Title: Criterion-Referenced Test Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Geoffrey T. LaFlair
Maintainer: Geoff LaFlair <gtlaflair@gmail.com>
Description: Contains methods for criterion-referenced test analyses as 
    described by Brown & Hudson (2002) in Criterion-referenced Language 
    Testing (ISBN: 9780521000833). This includes cut-score item discrimination 
    analyses and measures of dependability.
URL: https://github.com/gtlaflair/rcrtan
BugReports: https://github.com/gtlaflair/rcrtan/issues
Depends: R (>= 2.10)
License: GPL-3
LazyData: TRUE
Imports:
    dplyr,
    magrittr,
    purrrlyr,
    stats,
    tibble,
    tidyr
Suggests:
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder:
    knitr
RoxygenNote: 6.1.0
